Domain: web agent / Digital (Mind2Web proxy — WorkArena++ unavailable on HF)

Problem (truncated to 1500 chars):
Find the cheapest power supply unit with at least 600W power output.

Candidate v2 hierarchy:
{
  "global": "Search for power supply units with minimum 600W capacity and identify the lowest-priced option.",
  "subtasks": [
    {
      "subtask": "Navigate to and access product search interface",
      "atomics": [
        "Load the product search or shopping page",
        "Locate the product search input field or catalog view",
        "Confirm page has fully loaded"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Search for power supply products and apply power capacity filter",
      "atomics": [
        "Enter 'power supply' or 'PSU' in the search field",
        "Apply filter for minimum 600W power output",
        "Execute the filtered search query"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Extract product specifications and pricing from results",
      "atomics": [
        "Identify all power supply products in search results",
        "For each result, extract the power rating in watts",
        "For each result, extract the current price"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Filter and sort results to identify the cheapest option",
      "atomics": [
        "Retain only products with power rating >= 600W",
        "Sort retained products by price in ascending order",
        "Identify the product with minimum price"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Verify and report the final result",
      "atomics": [
        "Confirm selected product has power >= 600W",
        "Record the product name and exact price",
        "Output the cheapest power supply unit"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "global_atomics": [
    "Validate that at least one 600W+ power supply exists in filtered results",
    "Perform final sanity check on price claim against displayed values"
  ]
}

Candidate v2 gold_actions:
{
  "global": "Execute a web search workflow to locate and compare 600W+ power supplies, returning the cheapest match.",
  "subtasks": [
    {
      "subtask": "Navigate to product search by opening search page and waiting for DOM readiness",
      "atomics": [
        "Navigate to the shopping website homepage or catalog",
        "Locate the search box component via DOM query",
        "Verify search interface is interactive"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Search for 'power supply' and filter by wattage >= 600W using UI controls",
      "atomics": [
        "Type 'power supply' into the search input and submit",
        "Click the power/wattage filter control",
        "Select '600W' or 'greater than 600W' option",
        "Apply filters to reload results"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Parse product cards to extract power rating and price for each listing",
      "atomics": [
        "Iterate over all product result elements in the DOM",
        "Extract wattage text from each product card",
        "Extract price text from each product card"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Filter to 600W+ products and compute minimum price",
      "atomics": [
        "Convert extracted power strings to numeric wattage values",
        "Convert extracted price strings to numeric currency values",
        "Filter product list to wattage >= 600",
        "Find the product with minimum numeric price"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Validate the result and output the cheapest power supply",
      "atomics": [
        "Verify selected product wattage >= 600",
        "Confirm price is lower than all other 600W+ options",
        "Return product name, power rating, and price"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "global_atomics": [
    "Assert that filtered result count > 0 (at least one 600W+ PSU found)",
    "Double-check price value against displayed price on product page"
  ]
}

